Isolates displaying minimum inhibitory concentrations (MICs) of > 2 mg/l by Etest to cefpodoxime and/or MICs > 1 mg/l to any other ESCs were included (n = 54; 35 E. coli, 11 K. pneumoniae, and 8 K. oxytoca).
